<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<title>HTML Headings and Paragraphs</title>
<style>
body{font-family:Verdana,sans-serif;background-color:rgb(240,248,255);margin:20px}
h1,h2,h3{color:#2e7d32}
p{font-size:18px;color:#444;margin-bottom:15px}
.box{border:3px solid #2e7d32;padding:20px;margin-top:20px}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="box">
<h1>Main Heading</h1>
<h2>Sub Heading</h2>
<h3>Section Heading</h3>
